	<text xml:lang="de">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646" cert="high">Glaronense</placeName> negotium me valde cruciat; metuo, ne de ipsis sit actum, praesertim si a nostra parte nulla sentiant auxilia.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3494" cert="high">Nicolaus a Diesbach</persName> omnia mihi exposuit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Displicet nostris 1. das <placeName ref="l160" cert="high">Fryburg</placeName> und <placeName ref="l760" cert="high">Soloturn</placeName> auch bschriben uff den tag, 2. das die evangelischen Zuͦgwanten nitt bschriben, 3. das man zemmen sol kon und sich aber nitt erlüteren, was man thuͦn well, so man die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646" cert="high">Glarner</placeName> bi recht nitt wil bliben lon.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man meint, man schwige inen vil zlang; nahen sige es an anderen auch und bsonders an Zürich, diewyl sy sich vil mercken laßind nitt zuͦ lyden, das so vil da truckt werde wider iren glauben.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Darum guͦt, das man inen bi zyten seite, woran es glegen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Horum te admonere volui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nuper, cum cursor vester hic esset, non eram domi; nunc vix tantum datur, ut haec scribam.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1541">Herterus</persName> heri nobiscum fuit; ostendit mihi literas <persName type="citizen_name">Metzleri</persName> ad te, pro quo ad me etiam scribunt <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blaurerus</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Frisius</persName> et frater.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Ego vero nihil illi prorsus consulere possum nisi hoc:</foreign> Es hatt jetz juncker <persName type="citizen_name">Hartman von Hallwyl</persName> ein ledige pfrund uff dem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1615" cert="high">Bötzberg</placeName>, da <persName type="citizen_name">Leonhardus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name">Gervasii</persName> tochterman vor gsin.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Da acht ich, so er von üch dem junckeren commendiert wurde, welcher lehenherr da ist, er sölti in annemmen.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ir mögend da vil.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Sonst weiß ich imm weder zraten noch zhelffen.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec propere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te <persName type="auto_name">Diesbachius</persName>, <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Zehenderi</persName>, quęstores etc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta tuos omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 16. octobris 1560.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8018" cert="high">Hall[erus]</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino suo honorando et compatri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
